title: [Hang'em High]
description: Some branches have been noticeably sawed off of the trees in the area, culminating in several piles a distance aways.  Just beyond that area is a small wagon with lit windows that emanates the sounds of merriment.

Some branches have been noticeably sawed off of the trees in the area, culminating in several piles a distance aways.  A few workers labor tirelessly, whittling the wood down to pointed sticks.  Parked just beyond them is a small wagon with a dingy blue roof.
